        "C increases by 5",
        "C doubles",
        "C stays the same"
      ],
      "answer": {
        "type": "multiple_choice",
        "correct": "C increases by 5"
      },
      "difficulty": 1,
      "hints": {
        "default": [
          "Each time \\(n\\) goes up by 1, \\(C=5n\\) increases by 5×1.",
          "New \\(C=5(n+1)=5n+5\\).",
          "Change in \\(C = 5\\)."
        ]
      },
      "worked_solution": "\\(C=5n\\). Increasing \\(n\\) by 1 gives \\(C=5(n+1)=5n+5\\), an increase of 5."
